snippet.title: Official Trailer for Ranch Rush 2
snippet.description: After saving an ailing flower nursery in the original Ranch Rush, Sara sets her sights on some fun in the sun. Along with her new friend Coco, Sara embarks on a tropical farming adventure in this highly enjoyable sequel.
